10. WHAT THE CLIENT CONTROLS REALLY MEAN
==================================================

The end-user client has several controls that are easy to misunderstand. Here they are in plain language.

Problem description
- The actual strategic question.

Client context
- Extra background text the user pastes in.
- Right now, this is mostly a paste box, not a full file-management system.

