11. WHAT THE ADMIN APP REALLY CONTROLS
==================================================

The Admin side is where the operator shapes the product's intelligence.

In nontechnical terms, the operator is defining:

- what strategic knowledge exists,
- what realism-check knowledge exists,
- what kinds of practicality judges exist,
