13. DEPLOYMENT, INSTALLERS, AND LOCAL VS HOSTED MODES
==================================================

The codebase contains two deployment stories at once.


13.1 Hosted AWS mode

The newer and more clearly documented production path is:

- host the cloud server on AWS,
- keep PostgreSQL in RDS,
- keep Qdrant alongside the app on EC2,
- optionally use S3 for uploaded files,
- connect the Admin and Client desktop apps to that hosted server.

