16. THE MOST IMPORTANT MENTAL MODEL
==================================================

If you only remember one thing, remember this:

Hivemind is not just one app.

It is three connected layers:

1. a preparation layer,
2. an analysis engine layer,
3. and an end-user layer.

Preparation layer
- internal staff load the system with strategy knowledge, constraint knowledge, practicality judges, and simulations.

Analysis engine layer
- the server searches that knowledge, runs multiple AI roles, forces them to critique one another, combines similar conclusions, and rejects answers that fail practicality.

End-user layer
- a client submits a problem, watches the live process, and receives structured recommendations and reasoning.

That three-layer model explains most of the repository.


